entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Paying off the debt. Real or not Jabba feels you have one. At least you'll be able to call it square when you are done.
entries.journal_entry_description: Bib has you doing jobs to work off Jabba's animosity. Vourk has you doing the same to betray him. Hopefully in all of this you'll find what you want.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Vourk said Bib would be contacting you shortly.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Ahh...the troublemaker! Jabba is not pleased with you. Go see Niko. If you can help him do some jobs for Jabba it might buy you some mercy.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: See what the thug Niko wants. Vourk needs you to betray these guys, but what will you have to do until that moment comes?
